# Drush — PS Project

## Règle absolue

**Toutes les commandes Drush s'exécutent dans le conteneur `ps_php`.**

```bash
# Via Makefile (recommandé)
make drush-cr
make drush-uli
make drush-status

# Direct
docker exec -i ps_php sh -lc 'cd /var/www/html && vendor/bin/drush <command>'
```

Working directory dans le conteneur : `/var/www/html` (= `src/` sur l'hôte).

## Commandes fréquentes

```bash
# Cache
drush cr                          # Cache rebuild

# Configuration
drush cex -y                      # Export config → src/config/sync/
drush cim -y                      # Import config
drush cim --no --diff             # Preview import (sans appliquer)
drush config:status               # Config pending

# Base de données
drush updb -y                     # Mises à jour DB
drush sql:query "SELECT 1"        # Requête (PostgreSQL)

# Modules
drush pm:install ps_offer -y
drush pm:uninstall ps_demo -y
drush pml --status=enabled --no-core

# Migrations (ps_migrate)
drush migrate:status
drush migrate:import ps_offer_from_xml --update -y
drush migrate:reset-status ps_offer_from_xml

# Développement
drush uli                           # Login one-time link
drush watchdog:show --count=20
drush php:eval "echo 'ok';"

# PS custom
drush ps:dictionary:import -y       # Import dictionnaires
```

## Générateurs Drush (scaffolding)

```bash
drush generate module --answer=module=ps_example
drush generate plugin:block
drush generate form:config
drush generate service
```

## Config workflow (obligatoire avant commit config)

```bash
# 1. Exporter
make drush-cr  # ou drush cr
docker exec -i ps_php sh -lc 'cd /var/www/html && vendor/bin/drush cex -y'

# 2. Vérifier diff
git diff src/config/sync/

# 3. Commit atomique config + code associé
```

## Commandes Makefile métier

```bash
make dictionary-import    # drush ps:dictionary:import
make import-crm           # Pipeline migrate CRM
make import-status        # drush migrate:status
make index-solr           # Indexation Search API Solr
make deploy               # Workflow déploiement complet
```

## Scripts CLI

Workflow avancé : `bash src/scripts/main.sh <domain> <action>`

```bash
bash src/scripts/main.sh drupal install
bash src/scripts/main.sh drupal demo
bash src/scripts/main.sh tools build
bash src/scripts/main.sh tools check
```
